Just to come back.

20
00:01:14,093 --> 00:01:19,565
l just mean, sometimes l sort of forget
that he's gone. lt's, like, ''Where's Riley?''

21
00:01:20,253 --> 00:01:23,848
''Oh, wait, the Central Republic
of Where-ln-The-Hell.''

22
00:01:24,853 --> 00:01:26,969
Xander?

23
