lt's understandable, what with all the upset,
all that blamin' of innocent bystanders.

358
00:26:20,693 --> 00:26:23,253
- What?
- l mean, did she want to be made a fool of?

359
00:26:23,333 --> 00:26:27,246
And what does a person have to do
to make it right? Watch it, mate.

360
00:26:28,093 --> 00:26:31,130
On second thought, do whatyou like.

361
00:26:31,213 --> 00:26:33,283
Ale. Yes.

362
00:26:33,373 --> 00:26:35,284
Fragrant ale.

363
00:26:37,653 --> 00:26:40,565
