399
00:29:00,173 --> 00:29:03,529
Not in my heart. lt was only one wench.

400
00:29:04,253 --> 00:29:08,804
l had had a great deal of mead.
The next thing l know, l'm a troll.

401
00:29:11,213 --> 00:29:14,967
